reviewText: excellent acting, very well done. one of my favorite characters from prior seasons was Julianne Nicholson (Dr. DePaul)
This was not specified as "non zone / district 1" so it would not play on my US equipment. I returned it.
Didn't realize it was non-US version.  Of course it does not work in DVD player.
This product is for region 2/PAL. US is region 1. Says this in product description too. Awesome show!
It will not play in the U.S.  Is this a case of buyer beware?  Serious waste of money.
